2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FYHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI%2F&h=acedd95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/YHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳海水化淡廠工程項目<br />\n<br />\n擬建海水化淡廠將採用逆滲透技術，食水產量為每日13萬5千立方米，其後可擴展至每日27萬立方米，為本港供應百分之五至十的食水用量。第一階段將軍澳海水化淡廠工程將按設計 - 建造 - 經營合約安排實施。 承包商將負責海水化淡廠的詳細設計，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建造和運營。將軍澳海水化淡廠的第一階段建造工程計劃於2019年開始，並於2023年完成。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/water-resources/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Fwater-resources%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=51cc9bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/water-resources/desalination/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實，香港也有採用蒸餾技術的海水化淡廠，取址屯門並運作了 7 年，可惜由於油價大升令運作成本大增，最終停止運作並拆卸。而現在投入建造的將軍澳海水化淡廠將採取逆滲透技術來產水，原理是利用滲透作用讓海水過濾成淨化水。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>將軍澳海水化淡廠估計每日能產出 13.5 萬立方米食水，約佔整體食水供應約 5%。</strong></span></span>但水務署預料未來擴建後，化淡廠的每日食水產量將增加至每日 27 萬立方米。現時，第一階段工程預計在 2023 年完成並正式投入運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2519663/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%89%B9%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E9%A0%90%202023%20%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2519663%2F%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258C%2596%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%25BA%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%25A0%2590%25202023%2520%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=e0eeb21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2519663/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%89%B9%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E9%A0%90%202023%20%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n大家肯唔肯捱貴水，起10間海水化淡取代東江水........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"咁應該抽乾船灣淡水湖定萬宜水庫拎地起化淡廠？"},{"pid":"10b8ec84a5dd2ea0e563a38ff8203c8f9004ff84","tid":1954544,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:14:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836d472df5e1e266f3bb5ff235da8c6bfd04542f","tid":1954544,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"仲有再造水<br />\n<br />\n根本係香港政府想依賴中國, 日日昆香港人冇左大陸就唔得<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/30629/%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB-%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%86%8D%E9%80%A0%E6%B0%B4%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83-%E6%9C%9B2060%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%AA%E7%B5%A6%E8%87%AA%E8%B6%B3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F30629%2F%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%2587%25AA%25E4%25B8%25BB-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E5%2586%258D%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E9%25A0%2598%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583-%25E6%259C%259B2060%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25B6%25B3&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=f9e8aef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/30629/%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E8%87%AA%E4%B8%BB-%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E5%86%8D%E9%80%A0%E6%B0%B4%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E9%A0%98%E5%85%88%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83-%