f75b","tid":1954544,"uid":265416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:28:10.000Z","msg":"如果無明日大愚，起夠兩座又點話"},{"pid":"84ce5991270f6c9c07f2ab84ca9ebfc13cf7b5a9","tid":1954544,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d64ba91991f2e343a08531d696916e09e1fd8b60","tid":1954544,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"海水化淡廠建在哪裡 有足夠土地嗎<br />\n想達到足夠數量要起幾耐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"現有水塘區，抽乾水就係一大堆地<br />\n<br />\n有化淡廠咁2個巨形人造水塘區（船灣淡水湖、萬宜水庫）仲有冇保留價值<br />\n<br />\n如果唔保留就變相多左2塊大形地，仲有周邊一大堆樹林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a9468655942428b78cddfae3cc7e61ef258fb4","tid":1954544,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"最奇怪嘅地方係明明香港已經無工廠但用水反而越嚟越多"},{"pid":"aecc4dba9a1c86574803e07cdb204a0eff157948","tid":1954544,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab6b282f813daeddc733ebd9c4fb667695360658","tid":1954544,"uid":12086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"問題唔係我地肯唔肯 係傀儡政權仲會唔會同你諗自給自足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:32:23.000Z","msg":"根本好多野可以自給自足<br />\n係港共要製造香港靠中共既事實<br />\n<br />\n海水化淡好值得做 但而家會變到政治不正確<br />\n講都唔再講"},{"pid":"8547b32bd56fecae0e91196dd31a0b71b2b2d738","tid":1954544,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:33:02.000Z","msg":"多多都比 民生野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ea6d412859cc25634787092933fe4ac898f6ae","tid":1954544,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f620dce6158cf10815faf93f9a8d902780619296","tid":1954544,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd58a592c27541b8a6fccfc430d559604a5221da","tid":1954544,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e2058cab16210635000f0fa1f4332dfe0062cdae","tid":1954544,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:05:08.000Z","msg":"海水化淡既成本好浮 好睇燃料價值"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:16:09.000Z","msg":"依家世界主流係用reverse osmosis <br />\n相對過往流行嘅flash evaporation同multi-effect distillation用少好多能源架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"應該無人會再起蒸餾廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:34:07.000Z","msg":"中東國家唔怕燃料貴仲有起緊 thermal  desalination嘅化淡廠 貪佢操作同維修簡單方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc050fce6fb9e709b416d0410a11a420accf5416","tid":1954544,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"唔好只係focus係價格<br />\n仲有帶動相關技術產業發展<br />\n根本係一定要做"},{"pid":"9df26e8484ebf6cb8e4f84cbccac61ec9f7f2654","tid":1954544,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c051b876f2298b28693dbaf2e4516e67a930ca6c","tid":1954544,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e25509e2a3aff8e0df158b6c80fabb0571fbf6a8","tid":1954544,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:03:10.000Z","msg":"港大水資源技術與政策研究中心行政總監李煜紹博士分析，香港現時以「統包總額」方式購買8.2億立方米東江水，配合本地水塘，供水量足夠香港使用。即使將軍澳海水化淡廠機組落成，多數處於備用狀態。他指，水務署已訂立乾旱應變計劃，足以應對個別乾旱年份。<br />\n<br />\n香港供水完全自給自足是否可行？思匯政策研究所早前發表報告，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要興建多10座海水化淡廠才可取代東江水，按將軍澳海水化淡廠造價77億元計算，取代東江水需斥資770億元，較港深廣高鐵844億元略便宜。</span></span></strong>立法會文件顯示，海水化淡與東江水的價格差距不斷收窄。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>2018年海水化淡每立方米總成本13元，較東江水每立方米10.5元貴23.8%。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/YHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FYHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=83d7124e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191113%2FYHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI%2F&h=acedd95b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191113/YHMPIAKLB3OWN6W2A7LLATUSYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳海水化淡廠工程項目<br />\n<br />\n擬建海水化淡廠將採用逆滲透技術，食水產量為每日13萬5千立方米，其後可擴展至每日27萬立方米，為本港供應百分之五至十的食水用量。第一階段將軍澳海水化淡廠工程將按設計 - 建造 - 經營合約安排實施。 承包商將負責海水化淡廠的詳細設計，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建造和運營。將軍澳海水化淡廠的第一階段建造工程計劃於2019年開始，並於2023年完成。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/water-resources/desalination/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcore-businesses%2Fwater-resources%2Fdesalination%2Findex.html&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=51cc9bf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsd.gov.hk/tc/core-businesses/water-resources/desalination/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實，香港也有採用蒸餾技術的海水化淡廠，取址屯門並運作了 7 年，可惜由於油價大升令運作成本大增，最終停止運作並拆卸。而現在投入建造的將軍澳海水化淡廠將採取逆滲透技術來產水，原理是利用滲透作用讓海水過濾成淨化水。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>將軍澳海水化淡廠估計每日能產出 13.5 萬立方米食水，約佔整體食水供應約 5%。</strong></span></span>但水務署預料未來擴建後，化淡廠的每日食水產量將增加至每日 27 萬立方米。現時，第一階段工程預計在 2023 年完成並正式投入運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2519663/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%89%B9%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E9%A0%90%202023%20%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2519663%2F%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%258C%2596%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E5%2590%2588%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%25BA%25EF%25BC%2581%25E9%25A0%2590%25202023%2520%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%258A%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2581%258B%25E4%25BD%259C&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUoE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=e0eeb21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2519663/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E6%B5%B7%E6%B0%B4%E5%8C%96%E6%B7%A1%E5%BB%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E5%90%88%E7%B4%84%E6%89%B9%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%81%E9%A0%90%202023%20%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E9%81%8B%E4%BD%9C</a><br />\n<br />\n大家肯唔肯捱貴水，起10間海水化淡取代東江水........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"咁應該抽乾船灣淡水湖定萬宜水庫拎地起化淡廠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:37:59.000Z","msg":"可以共存"},{"pid":"5a433149a14c4c6356a780874cc6f587faa09c10","tid":1954544,"uid":192517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T02:43:41.000Z","msg":"可以<br />\n奶支官反對"}]}